    <string name="about_shesecure">About SheSecure</string>
    <string name="about_description">SheSecure is your all-in-one safety companion, designed especially for women. Whether you\'re commuting late at night, facing an emergency, or just want peace of mind — we\'re here. Real-time location tracking, instant SOS alerts, nearby help centers, and emotional support — all in one place.</string>
    <string name="about_mission">Our mission is simple: To use technology as a shield, a voice, and a helping hand — so every woman feels confident, safe, and heard at every step of her journey.</string>
    <string name="our_mission">Our Mission</string>
    <string name="mission_description">At SheSecure, our mission is to revolutionize women\'s safety by providing a user-friendly platform that connects women to real-time safety features, emergency contacts, and support services. We are committed to creating a safer environment by offering instant access to SOS alerts, location sharing, and emotional support, ensuring that every woman is empowered and protected in any situation.</string>
    <string name="mission_illustration">Mission illustration</string>
    <string name="our_vision">Our Vision</string>
    <string name="vision_heading">We created SheSecure because no woman should feel unsafe.</string>
    <string name="vision_description">Empowering women with the tools and resources they need to feel safe, confident, and in control. We envision a world where every woman, regardless of her location, has immediate access to support, safety, and guidance, enabling her to navigate the world with peace of mind and security.</string>
